flowchart TD
    PUSH[Push ou PR] --> LINT[Job lint<br/>ESLint]
    PUSH --> TC[Job typecheck<br/>tsc noEmit]
    PUSH --> TEST[Job test<br/>Jest coverage]
    LINT --> BUILD[Job build<br/>npm run build]
    TC --> BUILD
    TEST --> BUILD
    BUILD --> E2E[Job e2e-tests<br/>Playwright]
